,Recommended,292910,13771744,"Posted: 1 January, 2015",all,worlebird,"So much fun!  If you are a fan of the old classic LucasArts point-and-click adventure games (Day of the Tentacle, Sam and Max, the Monkey Island series, etc.) you should enjoy Deponia.  This game is absolutely the spiritual successor to those games.  Even at full price, this is worth it.  When on sale, it's a real steal!For those who may be confused by the titles, there are three Deponia games in the series - this one, ""The Complete Journey"" is all three of those games combined seamlessly into one package (you don't get three individual games, rather the three games flow into each other one after the other).  So if you get this game, you do not need to get the three individual Deponia games."
